{"tid":1545482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人手置頂] 今晚7點半 太子站！！！","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T05:27:44.000Z","uid":44557,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2f024d1fa337771a1bf9ec1e009c8cdc6653d9","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚7點半太子站</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚7點半太子站</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚7點半太子站</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日得果兩三個post講緊831太子件事！求下你地暫時放一放低其他post唔好推住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第六日喇！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵聽日第一件事一定會走去剷哂啲cctv唔留證據</span></span>，咁我地就冇哂證據睇返太子係咪真係打死人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣對唔對得住係入面犧牲左既義士啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家屬極大可能已經被要脅唔出得聲！點解要佢地封口呀？因為呢個有可能係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>成個運動最大既核彈呀！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n件事疑點重重呀！你地睇返有巴打既整合啦！<br />\n<br />\n[大整合] 831事件未必得2個死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544367\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544367</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[有相有片]終極整合，831太子恐襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544831\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今晚 7點半<br />\n太子地鐵站<br />\n<br />\n要求黨鐵交出831太子站，石硤尾同荔枝角既cctv！將成件事還原真相呀！！！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/06/062949_72be70384414364a4032da6e08495638.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2F062949_72be70384414364a4032da6e08495638.pn