core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"831831831831831831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚今晚今晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7點半7點半7點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太子站呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b76b2f935779a18c4a20f50c90a549c21fd8442","tid":1545482,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"906 太子獻花 遮打反黑警 907 機場交通測試 908 美領集會 913 獅子山人鏈"},{"pid":"db61021ce2a5634760009b51d51326d94b709bf1","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"831 831 831"},{"pid":"c6069992bb5520a0bbd3aaa7ac846241ad0ae9e9","tid":1545482,"uid":221205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9ae02ad0a8dcb54916d5dd542d19b8833e299ad","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"屌你地有冇人性架 今晚7點半太子呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545147\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2eceeda859512fd06c0bb93f1982ff7201b7961c","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:33:30.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6e5b287ee2063c0cfec831e9fbdb0287a46ffdd4","tid":1545482,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>中英聯合聲明的謬誤</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若果一件物件是從來未曾擁有過，拿到手上是談不上「恢復」及「收回」的。同樣道理，1997年前中華人民共和國從來未曾對香港行使過主權，如何談得上「恢復行使主權」？中華人民共和國的漢族（即「中國人民」）從來也沒有擁有過香港，試問又如何「收回」香港？<br />\n<br />\n因此，中華人民共和國取得香港的土地應該形容為「兼併」或「呑併」。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>不平等條約無效論是謊言</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如兩國以和平條約（Peace Treaty）終止戰爭，而某些領土由一國割讓予另一國，則在國際法中亦被視為透過割讓（Cession）而取得主權。過去的國際法觀點認為，以戰爭解決國與國之間的爭議屬國家的權利，而「和平條約」的作用是令交戰雙方以某些條款（包括部份領土的轉讓）為代價以終止戰爭。因此，按照「時空性原則」，1842年及1860年割讓香港島及九龍半島均符合當時的國際法。<br />\n<br />\n國際法中，領土的轉讓只有是否合法，而沒有平等不平等。<br />\n<br />\n在中華人民共和國成為國家之前，英國已經從清帝國手中符合國際法地取得香港的主權。另一方面，中華人民共和國亦從來沒有繼承過清帝國的仼何權益。因此，《中英聯合聲明》中所謂「對香港恢復行使主權」的「恢復」根本無從談起，並且只是一個猜想。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cbwr6sW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbwr6sW.png&h=7ee87500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPAHEN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPAHEN9.png&h=e166e8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知情不報者 你地都係半個兇手！<br />\n你唯一可以做就係站出黎 講個真相比全香港市民聽！ ！ 還死者一個清白！</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肛犬：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n別再喱係電視後面，敢就走出黎攞出CCTV之類証據黎証明831冇人死冇人重傷囉仆街共狗！！！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/05/104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg&h=7d68f7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必問：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾倍OT收，係咪仲要&quot;好合理要屌埋女示者&quot;咁辛苦？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<br />\n民主斬件，仲當我傻！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，未贏收科？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非你係個班那埋護照旁身嘅扮民霸權，永續利益獨賣囉！！！</span></span></span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"c6d93c21eebeccf016ab5f68a9e639532b515d5f","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c5c4f7344b93d213a54403c236b4ad3ba1df636e","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無今晚文宣圖？</span></span>"},{"pid":"91783c7b74a6572d84cd61079a605092f82cef4b","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無今晚文宣圖？</span></span>"},{"pid":"4e40e73862b65fe0436c48e094b491f930981666","