lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84HytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=49a7a79b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"e31dc0ae1392fcc0cca670dcb9a416f0f8277df7","tid":1545482,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">大個仔</span>獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈<span style=\"font-size: small;\">內容包括</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"72ae46adc3a5f2e71e141437d3bc80acf4cc501c","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無今晚文宣圖？</span></span><br />\n9/10"},{"pid":"6449fa6102e1a842fc99566d04b47862a4af5dab","tid":1545482,"uid":221205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44e5fd27a5d18c4906a8fe227cdbf08ea87b1d00","tid":1545482,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f836ea14d49e54201a3246f610c8a6d645678a68","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無今晚文宣圖？</span></span><br />\n10/10"},{"pid":"cc1d642e4d42847a5f5c9f45b718d8d7806c7176","tid":1545482,"uid":11073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2eed2ee0e05bdcaeb545cdafb926e672316eac","tid":1545482,"uid":221205,"like":0,