快星期6會被刪除<br />\n我地要有一次大集氣出太子 制造輿論壓力<br />\n將831死人嘅概念植入市民心中<br />\n令全港市民聚焦落黨鐵 迫佢交831嘅CCTV<br />\n絕對唔係要依兩日咁得幾十人圍太子警署咁<br />\n一定要上千人<br />\n實行將太子站鋪滿白色鮮花<br />\n<br />\n若然屬實 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日就係手足頭七</span></span><br />\n依家號召各位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花</span></span><br />\n見字嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">巴打幫手spread出去</span></span> 一個人真係推唔起<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0eLgNaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0eLgNaX.jpg&h=ec9aaa6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【831】9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花行動post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544326\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544326</a>"},{"pid":"6dafaae9abe065ed63476097c23254087ac5de1e","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無今晚文宣圖？</span></span>"},{"pid":"04b2ce4ff60a8479d3d06dbb89f79e4038b4c472","tid":1545482,"uid":284940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">判林鄭落地獄<br />\n光復香港秩序</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qc1S47m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQc1S47m.jpg&h=52f5d3de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f875716a73f876bd4549cf21cd693647924d8806","tid":1545482,"uid":150267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5c4f7344b93d213a54403c236b4ad3ba1df636e","tid":1545482,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有無今晚文宣圖？</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFPM9z